sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend as Frontend
    participant Backend as Flask Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant JWT
    
    User->>Frontend: Enter userid/password
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/auth/login {userid, password}
    Backend->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE userid=?
    alt Valid credentials
        DB-->>Backend: User record
        Backend->>JWT: Generate JWT token
        JWT-->>Backend: Signed token
        Backend-->>Frontend: {success:true, token, userId}
        Frontend->>User: Login success
    else Invalid
        DB-->>Backend: No user or wrong password
        Backend-->>Frontend: {success:false, message:'Invalid credentials'}
        Frontend->>User: Error message
    end
    Note right of Backend: bcrypt password check + JWT with 7-day expiry

